  "texts": [
    "For BERTScore we use the suggested model microsoft/deberta-xlarge-mnli.",
    "We conducted an annotation study to assess the correlation between human annotators and LLMs as annotators.",
    "In this study, we asked the annotators and LLMs to annotate a subset of responses generated by Vicuna-SFT from the test dataset.",
    "The aim was to measure the level of agreement between the human annotators and each LLM annotator.",
    "Specifically, we assigned six human annotators and three LLMs to assess 48 generated responses."
  ],
